docs.title: Installation
docs.text: To use this application, you need to have Git and Doxygen installed on your computer. The console application is built using .NET Core Self-Contained Deployment, which allows it to run on MacOS, Linux, and Windows platforms. No setup is required; simply download and extract the files to a folder of your choice.

docs.title: Usage
docs.text: You don't need to install any plugins. You can download it for all platforms from the Releases window.

docs.title: Features
docs.text:
• It helps you to send the text in the specified .txt securely by encrypting it with the help of a key.

  • It helps you to use the encrypted file securely by decrypting the encrypted file with the help of a key.

  • You can also produce disposable keys.
